title: Yetiblack - Agency EP (2014)
description:
Agency is the first EP released by Yetiblack.


Track List:

1.  Chasm  5:51
2.  Optimism Only Serves the Future  5:46
3.  Shells of Our Youth  8:11


Yetiblack is a rock-post-rock band hailing from Granada in southern Spain with an international lineup drawing upon a diverse range of influences.  Started in 2012, 'Agency' is its first release clocking in at just under 20 minutes.  With dynamic songs combining elements of experimental post-rock, grunge, folk, and alternative the band seeks to infuse much needed creativity and variety into the local and national scene.
